# Language converter C - OpenScop
        - Description
                Uses a small C program to convert from C to OpenScop using CLAN

        - Compile
                $ make

        - Run examples
                $ make exec

        - Clean
                $ make clean

# Language converter Python - OpenScop
        - Description
                Based on the OpenScop and CLAN documentation builds a Python representation of the code and bulks it on OpenScop format

        - Run all unit tests
                $ python nose_tests.py

        - Run a single unit test
                $ cd ${class_folder}
                $ python ${class_name}_class.py

        - Run examples
                $ python converter_py2scop.py

        - Clean
                $ find . -name "*.pyc" -delete

# NOTES:
        - Python unit tests use the unittest module
        - To launch all unit tests you require NOSE (available through pip install nose)

